## Event Overview

Lucius is unlocked through a Legendary Release Event, where players earn points by clearing battles across multiple tracks and requirements.

## Event Goal

The goal is to earn enough points to unlock Lucius.

If you do not unlock him during the current event, your progress is saved and will continue when the event returns.

## Requirements and Tracks

Each track contains different restrictions and scoring opportunities.

The best teams usually balance:

* Requirement coverage
* Survivability
* Damage output
* Character availability
* Long-term roster value

## Team Planning

This guide focuses on practical teams that can score well without relying only on perfect end-game rosters.

Some teams may prioritize single high-value requirements, while others stack multiple requirements when the characters are strong enough to survive.

## Long-Term Strategy

Legendary Release Events reward preparation.

Characters that perform well in LREs often have value across other modes, especially healers, durable tanks, summoners, and flexible damage dealers.
